# 1. 摩耗する心

Mafuyu: (That's it for Modern Japanese. Which just leaves math...)
Mafuyu: (I should be able to solve this correctly as long as I follow this formula and don't make any calculation errors.)
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (Was that just my imagination...?)
Mafuyu: Where was I? Um...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (Oh no...)
Mafuyu: (Lately, my concentration's been breaking over the smallest noises.)
Mafuyu: (I struggled to focus even during finals the other day...)
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu's Mother: Mafuyu?
Mafuyu's Mother: ...
Mafuyu's Mother: Maybe I was imagining things...
Mafuyu: (Mom must've been checking to see how I was doing... Because she's worried about me...)
Mafuyu: (At least I think so, but...)
Mafuyu's Mother: How are your studies going, Mafuyu?
Mafuyu: Oh, um... Fine. I should be able to get through everything that I need to do today.
Mafuyu's Mother: Wonderful. That's my daughter.
Mafuyu's Mother: However, it's getting late, so why don't you find a good spot to wrap things up? You need your rest.
Mafuyu's Mother: You can always wake up early tomorrow morning to finish the rest. Also, here's some warm milk.
Mafuyu: Thank you. This is nice...
Mafuyu's Mother: Hehe. I'm glad to hear that.
Mafuyu's Mother: Speaking of which, you'll be getting your finals back tomorrow, right?
Mafuyu's Mother: I'm looking forward to seeing good results since you studied so hard for them.
Mafuyu: Yes, me too...
Mafuyu's Mother: Hehe. Anyway, please try to go to bed soon. Good night.
Mafuyu: Good night.
Mafuyu: It's almost 25:00...
Mafuyu: (The others are probably working right now...)
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (I should sleep... But I'm still nowhere near finished.)
Mafuyu: I'll keep working on these for a little while longer...
Teacher: I'll be returning your finals now. Please come up when I call your name.
Classmates: Okay.
Teacher: Next, Asahina.
Mafuyu: Coming...
Mafuyu: Oh...
Mafuyu: (I did worse than I thought...)
Mafuyu: (What do I do...?)
Mafuyu's Mother: I'm looking forward to seeing good results since you studied so hard for them.
Teacher: Asahina? Is something wrong...?
Mafuyu: N-No. Nothing's wrong.
Teacher: To be honest, Asahina, you made quite a few more mistakes than usual. Is everything okay...?
Mafuyu: Oh...
Mafuyu: Yes, everything's fine...
Teacher: Really? Well, my door's always open...
Mafuyu: Yes... Thank you...
Mafuyu: I'm back.
Mafuyu's Mother: Welcome home, Mafuyu. Do you get your finals back?
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: No, the teachers are apparently very busy and need a little more time to grade them.
Mafuyu's Mother: Oh, I see... I understand they have tough jobs, but I hope they finish grading them soon.
Mafuyu: *Nod*
Mafuyu: (I couldn't tell her about how I really did...)
Mafuyu: (But I won't be able to hide that forever... I should tell her sooner rather than later.)
Mafuyu: (I should... But...)
Mafuyu: (I'm afraid of what she's going to say when she sees that my grades are starting to slip.)
Mafuyu: (Not just say... What she might do...)
Mafuyu: (And I have another mock exam coming up.)
Mafuyu: (Doing well on that might make up for how I did on my finals...)
Mafuyu: If I can do that...
